summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 45E, page 119, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Burke's 2nd Addition, Lots 5, 6, 7 & 8, Block 13; Lots 1, 2, 11 & 12, Block 14; Lots 5 & 6, Block 18; and Lots 15 & 16, Block 17, Wood's Suppl. to Burke's 2nd Addition, located on both sides of Jackson St. from 28th Ave. So. to midblock east of 29th Ave. So. as Community Business (BC) Zone.
